{
  "stem": "7684.1",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The train stopped at a beautiful railroad station where little houses had little flowers and geraniums.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and we didn't think it was-- but you could see through the little window, where you had a chance to look-- when everybody wants to look.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they throwed open this door.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was a screaming and hitting with whips.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Out!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Out!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Out!",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We all stumbled out of this big door-- you understand-- from the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And little children got lost from the parents.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And there was a little trolley that came on what is in coal mine-- this little trolley what goes over.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there they throwed in the old woman and children what got lost from the parents-- they throwed them in there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that went straight to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were-- there was a trolley, and that went straight to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were just very scared.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Somehow, all the Germans-- SS stayed on the side.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I told you before, when we stayed together with these little-- with all these girls from-- the youngest was 16, and I was one of the oldest, from 20, I think.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was in between 20 years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we pass these Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And before we pass the Germans, we had our backpack.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Everybody has the backpack.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have to throw away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And one woman throwed away her backpack, and her baby fell.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And she said, oh, my baby!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that scene-- I remember-- remember that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the German hit him with a whip.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the blood was streaming from the face.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he say, I will take care of the baby.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he put his dog in the trolley, and it went right away to the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we passed these Germans.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
